data.title: Papal Audiences in 2024.02
data.text:
Cardinal Celestino Aós Braco, O.F.M. Cap., Cardinal-Priest of Ss. Nereo ed Achilleo, Metropolitan Archbishop emeritus of Santiago (Chile) and former President of Episcopal Conference of Chile

Archbishop Giorgio Lingua, Titular Archbishop of Tuscania and Apostolic Nuncio to Croatia

Cardinal Arthur Roche, Cardinal-Deacon of S. Saba, Prefect of Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments and Bishop emeritus of Leeds (England)

Archbishop Vittorio Francesco Viola, O.F.M., Secretary of Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments, Archbishop ad personam and Bishop emeritus of Tortona (Italy)

Bishop Aurelio García Macías, Titular Bishop of Rotdon and Undersecretary of Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments

Msgr. Krzysztof Marcjanowicz, Priest of Kraków (Poland), Undersecretary of Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments, Papal Master of Ceremonies of Office for the Liturgical Celebrations of the Supreme Pontiff and Chaplain of His Holiness

Cardinal Robert Francis Prevost, O.S.A., Cardinal-Deacon of S. Monica, Prefect of Dicastery for Bishops, President of Pontifical Commission for Latin America and Bishop emeritus of Chiclayo (Peru)

Archbishop Franco Coppola, Titular Archbishop of Vinda, Apostolic Nuncio to Belgium and Apostolic Nuncio to Luxembourg

Archbishop José Avelino Bettencourt, Titular Archbishop of Novigrad, Apostolic Nuncio to Equatorial Guinea and Apostolic Nuncio to Cameroon

Bishop Lizardo Estrada Herrera, O.S.A., Titular Bishop of Ausuccura, Auxiliary Bishop of Cusco (Peru) and General Secretary of Latin American Episcopal Council
